<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink338">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi cāra</l>
<l>lilaiyila malarnta vōṅkunilai yilava</l>
<l>malaiyuṟu tīyiṟ curamutaṟ ṟōṉṟum</l>
<l>pirivaruṅ kālaiyum pirita</l>
<l>larituval lunarnaṅ kāta lōrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Alas! May you live long, my friend! </l>
<l>Parting is difficult, even during this season of rare farewells, </l>
<l>when tall Silk Cotton trees, blooming leafless on the slopes, </l>
<l>blaze like fire upon the mountains.  </l>
<l>[Indeed,] our lover is strong! </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
